  "keyFeatures": [
    "Six-degree-of-freedom (6DOF) flight simulation",
    "Real-time altitude, velocity, and acceleration display",
    "Automatic design optimization",
    "Multi-stage and clustered motor support",
    "Extended Barrowman stability computation (CG and CP)",
    "3D rocket visualization and OBJ export for 3D printing",
    "Drag and stability analysis per component",
    "Configurable simulation plots and CSV export",
    "Custom simulation listeners and expressions",
    "Import/export to RockSim (.rkt) and RASAero II (.cdx1) formats",
    "Built-in motor database from ThrustCurve.org",
    "Cross-platform (Windows, macOS, Linux) Java application"
  ],
